{"tid":1124913,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"女大學生睇完《復仇者聯盟4》嚎啕大哭　胸悶難受雙手痙攣送院急救","createTime":"2019-04-25T10:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T10:24:50.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"351c680bc11c0e7f418b2666ec4ec6c1374e5067","tid":1124913,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:21:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2335681/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2335681%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=6325d18a\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2335681/?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n全球影迷都十分期待的《復仇者聯盟4 :終局之戰》（Avengers:Endgame）4月24日上映，不少Marvel粉絲為免被劇透，在上映首日已去觀看。內地一位女大學生，看完《復仇者4》後因傷心過度痛哭，最後竟引致胸悶及痙攣，要送院急救。<br />\n<br />\n浙江寧波一名21歲的女大學生昨日與朋友去看《復仇者聯盟4 :終局之戰》後，受劇情影響而忍不住嚎啕大哭，悲傷的情感，散場時仍沒有緩解。該女大生散場後感到胸悶，四肢開始麻木，更出現痙攣現象，五隻手指完全打不開，猶如「雞爪」。<br />\n<br />\n她被送醫院檢查後，當地醫生袁麗豔表示：<br />\n<br />\n考慮她是哭得太傷心，一直大口喘氣，造成了過度換氣。通過安撫讓她情緒放鬆，同時吸氧和戴口罩，減少過度換氣，就緩解了。<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言指她「入戲太深」、「無法理解」，但亦有網民表示自己在戲院同樣喊到頭痛，憋着一直啜泣，同樣覺得有點缺氧。"},{"pid":"06cc15a0aab88f99df147983d10d1d5a99417b37","tid":1124913,"uid":137018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82968d2ddf06d9d7d7a7ab8b7b970c4192dc2e79","tid":1124913,"uid":166452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"睇流浪地球下話"},{"pid":"56ba547a19c9eb921391971c755ad7d56822452d","tid":1124913,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d0b73acaff2054d7f78a6eea2bf435669fb5ab","tid":1124913,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxGcMe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxGcMe5.jpg&h=d3734ed3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3bb49110add184a8cf54fcadedb32576178b3db","tid":1124913,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}